data.title: #TOURNOTES: NIC VON RUPP PORTUGAL WILD CARD
data.description: After three years of narrowly missing out on the coveted wild card spot into the Portugal event, Nic Von Rupp sealed the deal with a 9.5 in the trials. With a coffee, a ham and cheese sandwich, and nothing to lose, Nic sets his sights on Supertubos for the start of the Moche Rip Curl Pro.

data.title: HURLEY H2O PRESENTS: SAMMY THE EXPLORER
data.description:
Meet Sammy, a local Sumba boy with mind for change. Working with Hurley H2O ambassadors Kai Hing and Marlon Gerber, Sammy's community now has a new well and access to clean drinking water. 

The best part? Sammy is one of many across Sumba that Hurley H2O and SurfAid Sumba were lucky to have helped.
